    <note>Fan(2) Rouzhong [24923] Yuanfu coalition. His name does not appear in the Jiangxi TZ jinshi list. Since the jinshi of some other Yuanfu and Yuanyou coalition members do not appear to be listed, it is possible that, depending on the date of the jinshi stele, that coalition members were not recorded. Rouzhong was a professor of the Spring and Autumn Annals (Chunqiu), which probably partly explains his disgrace. In 1135, on the basis of Yan(5) Dunfu's [2074] words, Rouzhong was given a posthumous office and one of his sons was given office. CBD, 2, 1662.</note>
